18#include "ODUPCAReader.h"
19#include "Result.h"
20
21#include <utility>
22
23namespace ZXing {
24namespace OneD {
25
26static Result MaybeReturnResult(Result&& result)
27{
28 const std::wstring& text = result.text();
29 if (!text.empty() && text[0] == '0') {
30 result.setText(text.substr(1));
31 result.setFormat(BarcodeFormat::UPC_A);
32 return std::move(result);
33 }
34 else {
35 return Result(DecodeStatus::FormatError);
36 }
37}
38
39Result
40UPCAReader::decodeRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row, std::unique_ptr<DecodingState>& state) const
41{
42 return MaybeReturnResult(_reader.decodeRow(rowNumber, row, state));
43}
44
45Result
46UPCAReader::decodeRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row, BitArray::Range startGuard) const
47{
48 return MaybeReturnResult(_reader.decodeRow(rowNumber, row, startGuard));
49}
50
51BarcodeFormat
52UPCAReader::expectedFormat() const
53{
54 return BarcodeFormat::UPC_A;
55}
56
57BitArray::Range
58UPCAReader::decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin, std::string& resultString) const
59{
60 return _reader.decodeMiddle(row, begin, resultString);
61}
